N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 358.2 - Applicability

State Regulations

This Part shall be applicable to every county, monitor, and
operator, and shall govern qualified manufacturers and installation/service
providers as to use, installation, and reporting with respect to ignition
interlock devices imposed upon the aforementioned criminal court population
within New York State. Notes
